GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Differentiators> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Differentiators> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Differentiators> ;
    narr:childCount "42"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "6ef54f1677d04a6730909411217ebc64079a3353" ;
    narr:narration """The competitive positioning of aswritten has evolved from a feature-set to a focus on [decision archaeology](narr:Narrative_MoneyAnswerDecisionArchaeology) and [provenance-backed trust](narr:Narrative_ProvenanceCitationMoment). The enterprise hook remains [cross-repo, cross-platform, org-owned memory](narr:Narrative_CrossRepoMemoryEnterpriseHook), which addresses the limitations of repo-scoped tools like Copilot. A central tension persists in the shift from synthesis to a [citation engine](narr:Narrative_CitationEngineNotSynthesis), which preserves specific methodology rather than collapsing it into generic platitudes. This is reinforced by [module layering](narr:Narrative_ModuleLayeringComposability), allowing for the compounding of distinct worldviews, and [introspect surfacing](narr:Narrative_ProductSurfacesOwnRoadmap), where the tool actively identifies its own knowledge gaps. Recent developments include a structural parallel between [design-token extraction](narr:Narrative_DesignTokenPerspectiveParallel) and perspective extraction, while the firm maintains that [storing the decision process](narr:Narrative_StoreDecisionProcessNotArtifact) is the primary value-add over archiving static artifacts. The trajectory frames collective memory as foundational infrastructure, analogous to [GitHub](narr:Narrative_GitHubAnalogy).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ArchaeologyQueryUseCase> ;
